title: Wrestling Observer Radio 7/19: Battleground PPV, Kevin Owens, Un
description:
Sunday, 19 July 2015 22:49 


Wrestling Observer Radio with Bryan Alvarez and Dave Meltzer is back today to talk all the news in wrestling and MMA including a full recap of the WWE Battleground PPV with thoughts on all the matches and angles, Kevin Owens' loss, Undertaker's return, SummerSlam, what's up with Jushin Liger, UFC in Cowboy's Stadium, Jose Aldo saying he'll still use IV's, questions and more! A fun show as always so check it out~!
